    "Challenges and Open ProblemsIn this section, some challenges and open problems of E/E architectures are discussed.",
    "Co-design of Multi-networking MechanismsThe continual evolution of E/E architecture topologies and networking technologies poses a challenge in co-designing them in conjunction with multiple networking technologies and novel E/E architectures.",
